{"tid":1923072,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"必須要用運動初期外國文宣嘅規模向全世界國家澄清：支那係武漢肺炎嘅罪魁禍首","createTime":"2020-03-13T01:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T12:14:39.000Z","uid":66260,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d82a4fc128b1c3fda988c616fc84cd221cdc63ee","tid":1923072,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T01:51:00.000Z","msg":"支那而家已經開始攻勢，不斷話武肺係外國傳入<br />\n面對一個咁無恥既政權唔可以掉以輕心<br />\n必須要向全世界澄清<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得運動初期我地點樣向全世界發聲？<br />\ntwitter攻勢，登報，街站<br />\n仲有唔少既外國盟友<br />\n要俾全世界知道，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那係一個爆發病毒，控制不力，事後推卸責任嘅下賤國家，必須全球圍剿</span></span>"},{"pid":"3daef94c37158a645bb3996e13851375e8408611","tid":1923072,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"如果今次俾支那做到救世主, 外國戰線就正式壽終正寢, 香港人以後唔會有運行"},{"pid":"bb0b3cf1cbe37782722638e71bebae3377b2fd0a","tid":1923072,"uid":51057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"登報有冇得諗?"},{"pid":"f84186686fafcfcab63b0cc95a8840ca036bd10f","tid":1923072,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ecd30a96e913a167756e44f6c88271c4f8b457","tid":1923072,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲天災用嚟宣傳，恐怕有反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5466e9747005424985271285de2b357b83889296","tid":1923072,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23ecd30a96e913a167756e44f6c88271c4f8b457","tid":1923072,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲天災用嚟宣傳，恐怕有反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj