moji\" />"},{"pid":"a74bb87a5590b68867d957cd54600009929a1a07","tid":1923072,"uid":44646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"咬實佢，係中共唔俾醫生公報疫情<br />\n係佢怕影響過年氣氛而壓制消息<br />\n至今仍在限制醫生發聲"},{"pid":"9f7d63c7b2d0261ee8cd1f6b50284c2bdfb73446","tid":1923072,"uid":44646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58e10539bc1d06ee3c760b6fe412ff8881c0a477","tid":1923072,"uid":158996,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:56:10.000Z","msg":"兩個方向<br />\n<br />\n一. 澄清病毒源頭係中國武漢<br />\n<br />\n二. 指出中國先買斷國際物資，再以救世主身份送物資，係極其可恥嘅行為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"第二有保留---自保手段無可厚非<br />\n(民主政府一樣會做)<br />\n<br />\n問題係佢個獨裁體制<br />\n會限制消息流通<br />\n令世界失去抗疫黃金時間"},{"pid":"b2ca557b4853b352986b67a0506d5faf0fea4e75","tid":1923072,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:00:09.000Z","msg":"早在2019.11月17已有武漢新沙士, <br />\n隱瞞疫情100%confirmed，華大媽都自己爆響口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6vjLHx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6vjLHx.jpg&h=b6ff0566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年央視新聞影片已經報導發現&quot;新型冠狀病毒&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLnKcA7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLnKcA7.jpg&h=4852a6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共權威教授証實 疾控中心人員沾染蝙蝠血&amp;尿液<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ggrqLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ggrqLg.png&h=e85e72cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢市疾病預防控制中心（WHCDC）可能是病毒來源，稱這處疾控中心距離華南海鮮市場不到300公尺，實驗室曾捕捉蝙蝠研究冠狀病毒，更有研究員被蝙蝠血和尿沾染到，採取自我隔離14天。<br />\n這份報告提到武漢有2間實驗室，除了距離華南海鮮市場30公里、P4級的中科院武漢病毒研究所，另有距離海鮮市場僅280多公尺的武漢市疾病預防控制中心（WHCDC）。報告中引述官方資料，指武漢疾控中心曾從湖北省與浙江省捕捉蝙蝠作為研究之用，也提到負責研究的研究員曾遭到蝙蝠攻擊，自我隔離14天，也曾發生沾到蝙蝠尿而被隔離。<br />\n肖波濤曾在哈佛大學醫學院工作，並與美國西北大學有合作研究，多次獲國家自然科學基金，這篇報告也有該基金支持。報導也提到這一份報告並非在權威學術期刊發表，只發布在科學論文分享網站，不過，目前已找不到該論文。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctwant.com/article/37094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Farticle%2F37094&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=c924a977\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/37094</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yb4Ai2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyb4Ai2U.jpg&h=4f3266d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEJdP9A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEJdP9A.jpg&h=ae708fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食蝙蝠 野味日常<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16DELMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16DELMa.png&h=9a06b18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2teXxrb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2teXxrb.jpg&h=bec28c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCOpWQf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCOpWQf.jpg&h=b5569668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗問呀貴啦, 哩3種可能性都好強 有根有據"},{"pid":"10052ce9bd4afac073973ca434a8aaa80252a063","tid":1923072,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2bd07b4a770efa4b4ca6bfc1aa1ac6e30e395583","tid":1923072,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ecd30a96e913a167756e44f6c88271c4f8b457","tid":1923072,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲天災用嚟宣傳，恐怕有反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"有咩反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界會企番係中國個邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"你國家個個病到死死下<br />\n睇報紙頭版日日見到香港人同中國鬧交係咪中國責任，睇得多就會港豬心態政治嘢我唔想理，求真都廢時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e49a0058a711ee7ee7159